data.description:
This spacious 4-bed, 2-bath home is a gem just a short drive from OAKLEAF TOWN CENTER, offering a wealth of dining, shopping, and entertainment options.The home boasts an excellent floor plan, featuring an open Dining Room, Living Room, and Family Room with a cozy fireplace. With soaring ceilings and ample natural light, the living spaces feel welcoming and airy.

Step into the expansive fenced backyard, offering plenty of space for a potential pool. The eat-in kitchen is equipped with newer stainless steel appliances, perfect for cooking and dining.

The Owners Suite is a true sanctuary, complete with a walk-in closet and a spacious bathroom featuring a corner garden tub,

It's conveniently located near NAS and falls within the sought-after Clay County school zone. walk-in shower, and double sinks. The second bathroom has newer tile floors and a tub-shower combination.

Important updates include a roof that is approximately 5 years old, along with an HVAC system and water heater that are both less than 5 years old. Enjoy the peace and quiet of a cul-de-sac location, low HOA fees, and no CDD fees.

This property holds plenty of potential and is ready for you to make it your own. Don't miss the chance to make it yours today!
